I'm PREGNANT! Most people believe that I was jus sayin that so I didn't have to fight Candace. I'm not scared of Candace but I'm not putting my baby at risk over some dumb shit. Anyways... so many people have asked me so I thought I would finally make it public. I am 16 weeks & 3 days (as of right now)! I went to the Dr. yesterday hoping to find out what the baby is but they couldn't tell. I'm tryin to figure out how to put a picture of the ultrasound on here but I dont know how. My baby daddy's name is Corey. He is Jamaican! He's very tall and skinny. He has brown skin and honey colored eyes. He's funny and crazy. But of course you know him & Brandy don't get along. My due date is September 6, 2006. Right now we are living with my sister in Palm Coast, Fl which is about 20 miles from Daytona. He's only got one more class to go and he'll be done wit school. We met at the school I go to in O-Town. He's already got his job here in Palm Coast. We are fixin to move out of my sister's house into a nice house down the road. We are happy & in love but not like everyone else in Lake City, I don't plan on getting married anytime soon. We are hopeing for a boy because I don't want to deal with a girl. Well now it's out and hope to have a pic of the ultrasound on here soon!

Holla
Miranda

In Loving Memory of
Myrtis Mae "Chubby" Hall
"My Momma"
March 18, 1948 till April 08, 2005

Momma,
I miss you so much. It seems so fake that you could be gone from me. I'm not sure how to take all this. I'm not sure how I feel anymore. I  miss you so much, Momma. I want you to come home to me. I just want to tell you so many things before you go. Just a few more minutes, please. I love you so much. You were the best mother in the world. (Betcha never thought I'ld say that, huh?) It sucks that you won't see me get married, have kids, or even graduate from college. Everyone kepps telling me that you are right here with me everday. That just so hard to understand. I can't live without you. I need you so much. I feel like I'm going crazy. Nobody could understand this pain. How can someone so close and important to you just be gone one day... unexpected? I feel like dying sometimes! I just want you back so bad. I love you more than anything. I hope you know that. I can't wait to see you oneday soon in heaven. Be waiting on me!

I Love You!
"Your Baby Girl"
Miranda

I'm sitting in my Computer App. class and I'm so freaking bored. I mean I have completed all my work for the week and its only Wednesday! I have nothing to do...at all. I mean I'm literally sitting here frezzing cold with nothing to do. So I decide to say hello to all the people who read about my boring life. So ok hmmm... Sean and me have been fighting so much. Im so stressed out. I think I took on to much at one time. I mean last night I just cryed becasue I dont want to fight with him. I love him very much but I just do not know what to do. School is easy but when it comes to taking tests I'm not the brightest one in the class. I mean I pass all my labs with 100's. But on the last two tests I got a 72/c and a 36/f. Theres no "D"s here either. So hopefully I can bring it up. I'm going to study hard for this test on friday. I really need a 100 or atleast an "A". I'm coming to Lake City Friday to pick Sean up or hopefully he can meet me half-way. I think it would be best for him to come here because we prob. wont fight as much. Nichole is going to Port St. Luice this weekend so Sean and I will have time to our selves. I think maybe my other roommates are going home to. That would be nice for me and him to have that time. WE NEED IT! I love him so much and we've been together for 3 years almost (off & on) but I just dont know. I just want the fighting to stop. Im stressed out becasue BJ is a bitch. I mean Im down here stressed out because of her. She got me and here ditched me. I dont know anyone. I just dont know anymore. Last night I just wanted to quit and come home. I felt like I was having a breakdown. I was crying and just trippin out. But I know that being here is the best thing Ive done with my life in God knows how long. When I move back in 3 years I will be making atleast $18-20 an hour @ 20 years old. I think  thats really good for someone whos 20. I mean I have friends who are 20 and make like what Brandy? $6:50. Amanda has a child and shes only making about that too. So I'm proud of myself and I know that everyone else is proud of me especially my mom and dad. They give me the world right now. It's crazy. I mean I think they love me more now than ever. I dont know I guess Im just tripping out. If anyone has advice on how to release all my stress let me know. Well Ive written a whole lot so I'm out.

"Hollaaa"

Miranda
